text: One of the last few hawkers still retaining the old sch vibes. Food selection is good and food is very nice.

Always enjoy the food here at the food centre.
My favourite stalls are the white bee hoon, lor mee/chicken noodles, hainanese chicken rice and the vadai and jemput pisang.
A small hawker centre witt limited parking. Good variety limited. But the bak chor mee stall is very nice. Love the good quality ingredients and tasty soup.

Back here from Sengkang just for this bowl of delicious Lor Mee! Springy noodles,
Crispy fried fish, tangy garlic and sour vinegar. This is hands down one the best!

Small place with few stalls, but tasty food choices.
